divs: Sighting Details While outside in the evening, approx 9:00 p.m.noticed light object cross sky heading west. Thought at first falling star, butstopped aburtly and disappeared. Then reappeared heading north across sky atextreme speed and then disappeared. Shortly after witnessed airplane in samearea moving across sky southwest. Not sure what it was, wondering if anyoneelse witnessed event.
Summary: light moving across sky at high speed. disappeare
